> 2014](https://twitter.com/randhirktm/status/491079090036682753)

> C 是 Sonakshi Malik，已婚。童婚在尼泊爾十分盛行，政府為什麼無法阻止？pic.twitter.com/f70q8sOLmn
>
> — Randhir Chaudhary (@randhirktm) 2014 年七月廿一日

